refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;


  max_lifetime



    Sessions that have not updated for the last max_lifetime seconds will be removed.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns the number of deleted sessions on success, &return.falseforfailure;.
 Note this value is returned internally to PHP for processing.

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    7.1.0

     Prior to this version, the function returned &true; on success.
